## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ddba7-104">托管实体的生存期未绑定到表示它的.NET 对象的生存期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ddba7-104">The lifetime of a managed entity is not bound to the lifetime of the .NET object representing it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ddba7-105">提供程序可用于使用此特性标记的方法创建相应的托管实体的新实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ddba7-105">The provider can use the method marked with this attribute to create a new instance of the corresponding managed entity.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ddba7-106">方法参数应为类绑定构造函数的参数具有相同名称和类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ddba7-106">The method parameters should have the same name and type as the parameters of the class binding constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ddba7-107">此属性的使用的存储库中的 WMI 类注册没有任何影响。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ddba7-107">Use of this attribute does not have any affect on registration of the WMI class in the repository.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ddba7-108">仅在运行时使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ddba7-108">It is only used at runtime.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ddba7-109">下面的示例演示如何使用 ManagementCreate 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ddba7-109">The following example demonstrates how to use the ManagementCreate attribute.</span></span>  
  
```  
[ManagementEntity]  
public class ProcessInstance  
{  
     [ManagementKey]  
     public int Id;   
  
     [ManagementCreate]  
     public ProcessInstance StartProcess(string cmdLine)  
     {  
        ProcessInstance newProcess = new ProcessInstance(cmdLine);  
        newProcess.Start();  
        return newProcess;  
     }  
}  
```
